* Desmonus sees Zarduss pleasure in the title in which she used for him, yet 
still her mind dwelled on the hunger that ate at her in the pit of her 
stomach.
Yet, she listened to his words.
Hmm...exterminate? Without making them suffer slowly before their sparke 
departed from their body? How...dull.
But she also guessed that if you caught a Maximal then you could do what you 
wanted just as long as it was dead once you were done, and that suited her 
just fine.
A wicked smile developed across her lips.*

" Extermination? The only true fate for the Maximals."

* But as Zardus turned she followed, knowing that her place from now on 
would always be behind him as a loyal femm.
The walk from the lab but then she watches him turn and look at her, her 
optics watching every one of his movements.*

" My weapons will do me fine, Lord."

* And now, it was time to get to work and find herself a meal once the 
battle began.*
